sub_title: Campaign & Communication at International Campaign for Tibet Europe
summary:
Coach, Trainer & Mover
As a COACH and trainer I work with people who want to take the next step in their professional life and are ready to learn more about themselves. By increasing their knowledge about themselves and their (professional/social/cultural) environment, clients can take the lead in their career, their personal life and their overall happiness. Expertise with young professionals and entrepreneurs.

In TEAMS and ORGANIZATIONS I facilitate the process of strong team building and overall performance. Hereby focus is on trust-building activities, creating effective communication between team members and developing personal ownership. 

Next to traditional coaching methods I integrate (KICK)BOXING and strength training into my coaching programs. Understanding that body and mind are interrelated, moving is a great tool to get in touch with yourself and your belief-systems. The strength and confidence that is built here, will directly translate into other areas of life. 

I have a multicultural background (Tibetan/German) and worked with people in the townships in South Africa, slums in India, refugee camps in Greece as well as with young professionals and entrepreneurs in the Netherlands. I have seen many different ways in which life can be challenging and many ways in which these challenges can translate to growth. I am at home with questions around IDENTITY (being an expat, having a mixed cultural heritage, gender expectations etc.).

I work in English, Dutch and German and offer coaching and (sport)training face-to-face or online. 

If you are interested in joining my coaching program or want to get more information about me and my work please feel free to connect! 

E-mail: lai.schumann@gmail.com
